title: 后台刷屏报错
txt_content:
装上 【PixelmonEssentials】这个插件以后 后台就疯狂报错 下面是插件地址和后台的刷屏报错
[综合]PixelmonEssentials —— 宝可梦的基础插件,你值得拥有[1.12.2]
https://www.mcbbs.net/thread-921662-1-1.html
(出处: Minecraft(我的世界)中文论坛)

[ SYSTEM ] MCSM Console... 
[09:17:37] [World Spawner/ERROR]: Could not pass event ForgeEvent to PixelmonEssentials v1.2.9-public
